displayView

public void displayView(int position)
Opens the selected fragment as position. The fragments according to position are as below:
0 -> HomeListFragment (0 for the FragmentGetBoardingPasseFromBackend )
1 -> AccountListFragment
2 -> PastBoardingPassListFragment
3 -> HomeListFragment (3 for the FragmentAbout )

Parameters:
position - as in the drawer-list to choose the fragment as described above.

getResultFromActivity

public void getResultFromActivity(int requestCode,
                                  int resultCode,
                                  java.lang.String path)
Method to save the read barcode image (from PDF) as a boarding-pass in the local DB.
This method rotates the read-image in 3 other orthogonal angels & tries to read the barcode in all the 4 possible perspectives.

Parameters:
requestCode - not used
resultCode - not used
path - The bitmap-image's file path. The file is deleted after processing.
